{"tid":845043,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"AMD 7nm zen2 樣品出爐：頻率仍相較 8700k 為低！","createTime":"2018-10-02T10:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T13:58:21.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"896eb8ae60b624bff5130f46fae0eb33bb29dd76","tid":845043,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:48:06.000Z","msg":"國外論壇 HardOCP 一位網友 mockingbird 爆料（<a href=\"https://hardforum.com/threads/the-radeon-technology-group-rtg-has-received-its-first-zen-2-sample.1967802/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhardforum.com%2Fthreads%2Fthe-radeon-technology-group-rtg-has-received-its-first-zen-2-sample.1967802%2F&d=6dggj3QqVcJ%2F2O%2By4evOwJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=17f8d94c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hardforum.com/threads/the-radeon-technology-group-rtg-has-received-its-first-zen-2-sample.1967802/</a>），目前 RTG（Radeon Technology Group）已收到首款 Zen 2 架構處理器樣品。這是一顆 8 核 16 線程的處理器，具體規格不詳，可能是 Ryzen 7 3700X 這種主流旗艦產品。<br />\n<br />\n不過從洩露消息來看，測試結果似乎對 Intel 即將發表的第九代 Core 威脅不算很大，低於玩家的普遍期望值，讓盼望 AMD 能乘勝再敲 Intel 一棒的人感覺頗悶。<br />\n<br />\n這顆測試樣品的基礎／Turbo Core 時脈是 4.0 / 4.5GHz，要比目前 Ryzen 7 2700X（3.7 / 4.1GHz）高一些，不過仍舊相較 Intel 8700K 4.7GHz 的 Turbo Boost 時脈為低，更不及未來 9800K / 9900K 的 5GHz<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2018/10/02/amd-7nm-processor-sample/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2Famd-7nm-processor-sample%2F&d=6dggj3QqVcJ%2F2O%2By4evOwJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=ae7641c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2018/10/02/amd-7nm-processor-sample/</a>[/url]"},{"pid":"6190d262013730af6631fadef451013a223fc825","tid":845043,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國外論壇 HardOCP 一位網友 mockingbird 爆料（<a href=\"https://hardforum.com/threads/the-radeon-technology-group-rtg-has-received-its-first-zen-2-sample.1967802/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhardforum.com%2Fthreads%2Fthe-radeon-technology-group-rtg-has-received-its-first-zen-2-sample.1967802%2F&d=6dggj3QqVcJ%2F2O%2By4evOwJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=17f8d94c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hardforum.com/threads/the-radeon-technology-group-rtg-has-received-its-first-zen-2-sample.1967802/</a>），目前 RTG（Radeon Technology Group）已收到首款 Zen 2 架構處理器樣品。這是一顆 8 核 16 線程的處理器，具體規格不詳，可能是 Ryzen 7 3700X 這種主流旗艦產品。<br />\n<br />\n不過從洩露消息來看，測試結果似乎對 Intel 即將發表的第九代 Core 威脅不算很大，低於玩家的普遍期望值，讓盼望 AMD 能乘勝再敲 Intel 一棒的人感覺頗悶。<br />\n<br />\n這顆測試樣品的基礎／Turbo Core 時脈是 4.0 / 4.5GHz，要比目前 Ryzen 7 2700X（3.7 / 4.1GHz）高一些，不過仍舊相較 Intel 8700K 4.7GHz 的 Turbo Boost 時脈為低，更不及未來 9800K / 9900K 的 5GHz<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2018/10/02/amd-7nm-processor-sample/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2Famd-7nm-processor-sample%2F&d=6dggj3QqVcJ%2F2O%2By4evOwJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=ae7641c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2018/10/02/amd-7nm-processor-sample/</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"daa875a8d1cef6ad335e139a62ab2329a3f2b13a","tid":845043,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:50:28.000Z","msg":"mockingbird 爆料提到「Already Nibbing at the Core i7 8700K」，意指效能上已經咬住 8700K。鑑於 Ryzen 7 1800X 和 2700X 的基礎運算性能本就已經超過 8700K，磁盤 I/O 等性能也在伯仲之間，唯一讓人遺憾的就是 IF 總線帶來的高內存延遲副作用，因此這句話很有可能表示這顆測試樣品的內存延遲有改善。<br />\n<br />\n不過測試平台使用的記憶體為 DDR4 3600，目前二代 Ryzen 預設支援 DDR4 2933 記憶體，超頻支援 DDR4 3200~3600 也不算難事，因此這樣的記憶體支援也不算多勁爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。爆料還提及，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">測試平台頻繁發生系統當機，有些測試需要重啟多次才能完成</span></span>，以常規思路來看，很有可能是記憶體不穩定導致。<br />\n<br />\n總括來說，4.0 / 4.5GHz 的基礎／Turbo Core 時脈、使用 DDR4 3600 記憶體，以及（maybe）記憶體延遲看齊 8700K，從這些爆料消息來看，這顆樣品的表現確實算不上多驚豔，最大的心理落差來自時脈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。雖然未來還有繼續打磨提高時脈的空間，但從初代 Ryzen 測試樣品與正式發售產品的時脈對比來看，提升空間應該不大。"},{"pid":"846623dbd6de0b0f8f730af1af1e7bfe423a85fa","tid":845043,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:53:06.000Z","msg":"AMD 目前的 Ryzen 處理器雖然架構設計優秀，然而受制於格羅方德 14 奈米製程表現，Ryzen 能衝擊的最高時脈大幅低於 Intel 處理器：第七代 Core 的 Turbo Boost 時脈高達 4.5GHz，超頻「基本盤」高達 4.8GHz 甚至 5GHz，而 Ryzen 卻只能利用 Turbo Core 到 4.1GHz，超頻則普遍止步於 4.2GHz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">P.S. 我嗰粒 2700x 只能穩超4ghz，4.1ghz 開始不穩，4.2ghz 100%死機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，試問 8700k 有幾可體質會差到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</span>"},{"pid":"18a80cfc7628440a29eb56e83beffa167c77fb3b","tid":845043,"uid":85659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T11:06:18.000Z","msg":"仆街 真係4.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n消息都是真的<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">台GG真係咁快整到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</span>"},{"pid":"b4a13e48f9e91499fefed5b7dcaa6178b81ec5ec","tid":845043,"uid":58882,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T11:11:46.000Z","msg":"只係第一批es sample data 來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr